Rocco Di PIPPA, alias R. S. Long, alias Roxy Long, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6902. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. March 15, 1939. John J. Cohen, of Pittsburgh, Pa., for appellant. Charles F. Uhl, U. S. Atty., and John D. Ray, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Pittsburgh, Pa.

Before DAVIS, BIGGS, and MARIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
